### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This is one of my repositories, I use this page to upload my codes (well, it's coded under the team/group). The team contains of 7 students, 5 students (females) from Universitas Gadjah Mada and another 2 students (males) from Universitas Budi Luhur. Go to my GitHub page by clicking on "View on Github" button :D
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
